#

Herbed Mashed Potato Casserole

45 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main DishSide Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasyCasserole

Description

Creamy, herbed mashed potatoes baked to perfection with a crispy top.

Ingredients

  • mashed potatoes: 4 cups
  • cream cheese: 8 oz
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • chopped fresh herbs (like parsley, chives, and thyme): 1/4 cup
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 1 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
